          "sqlQuery": "SELECT\nID,\ntoday_delta_additions,\nBooking_Date,\nAgreement_Value__c,\nStatus__c,\nKUNNR,\nAccount_Mobile_Number__c,\nAccount_Mobile_1__c,\nMobile_Number__c,\nFirst_Name__c,\nLast_Name__c,\nProject_Text__c\nFROM `powerbi-implementation.dataWarehouse_prod.sales_booking`\nWHERE Status__c IN ('Booked', 'Processed')\n  -- processed\nAND Booking_Date IS NOT NULL",
